    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Phalangium yurisnegovoyi sp.n.: A—male body, habitus dorsal, B—female body, habitus dorsal, C—male eye tubercle, dorsal, D—male femur I, dorsal, E, F—male right chelicera (E—lateral, F—mesal), G, H—male right pedipalp (G— mesal, H—lateral), I, J—female right chelicera (I—lateral, J—mesal), K, L—female right pedipalp (K—lateral, L—mesal), M, N—penis (M—dorsal, N—lateral), O, P—Close-up of penis glans (O—dorsal, P—lateral), Scale lines: A, C—1 mm, D–N—0,5 mm, O–P—0,1 mm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6920279/files/figure.png" ;
